What information is present in logs ?
	[] Invalid Inputs
	[] Exeptions
	[] Auth failures/success
	[] Operations ( insert, delete , etc)
	[] Database access
	[] Suspect behaviours
	[] System Logs
	[] Http server logs

How are logs stored ?
	. SaaS (papertrail, loggly, ...)
	. Splunk
	...


